File 2: target.rs (Rust)
  Tree size: 156, depth: 9

Similarity Metrics:
  Cosine (histogram):    0.92
  Structure:             0.86
  Jaccard:               0.89
  Combined Score:        0.89

=== Documentation Comparison ===
  Doc count:    5 vs 4 (diff: -1)
  Doc lines:    24 vs 18 (diff: -6)
